sections.heading: to 2-124a. - Connecticut Competitiveness Council; membership; vacancies; duties; annual report
sections.text:
Sections 2-123 to 2-124a, inclusive, are repealed, effective July 1, 2023.

(P.A. 15-212, S. 1; June Sp. Sess. P.A. 15-5, S. 498; May Sp. Sess. P.A. 16-3, S. 21; P.A. 17-85, S. 1; 17-105, S. 4; P.A. 18-91, S. 13; P.A. 23-204, S. 444.)
